<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Freeride Bariloche</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;600;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
  background: black;
  color: white;
}

/* HERO CON TU FOTO */
.hero {
  height: 100vh;
  background: url('foto3.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 30px;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 2.5em;
  font-weight: 900;
}

.hero p {
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.btn {
  background: #ff3c00;
  padding: 12px 20px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/* GALERIA */
.gallery {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

.gallery img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 300px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

/* FRASE */
.section {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.section h2 {
  font-size: 2em;
}

/* CTA */
.cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 50px 20px;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

/* DESKTOP */
@media (min-width: 768px) {

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 4em;
}

.gallery {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
}

.gallery img {
  height: 400px;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div>
    <h1>BARILOCHE FREERIDE</h1>
    <p>No vengas a mirar. Vení a vivirlo.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/+5492944204802">Reservar</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FRASE -->
<div class="section">
  <h2>Esto no es turismo. Es experiencia.</h2>
</div>

<!-- GALERIA CON TUS FOTOS -->
<div class="gallery">
  <img src="foto1.jpg">
  <img src="foto2.jpg">
  <img src="foto3.jpg">
  <img src="foto4.jpg">
  <img src="foto5.jpg">
  <img src="foto6.jpg">
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="cta">
  <h2>¿Listo para vivirlo?</h2>
  <a class="btn" href="https://instagram.com/@bariloche_voy">Ver Instagram</a>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Freeride Bariloche
</footer>

</body>
</html>
